{"tid":219221,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"時間過得好快 感受唔到真實感","createTime":"2017-04-27T05:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T06:53:10.000Z","uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f1a96db44b00c9132946d932a2e10ef36abe1b","tid":219221,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"成日諗唔起今日係幾號 <br />\n搭車果陣 望住個天 依家係日頭 <br />\n好快又會變成夜晚 <br />\n咁樣循環既每一日 有d咩意義 <br />\n日期又有d咩意義? <br />\n個腦好似唔識諗野 做人好辛苦 <br />\n2017？乜野新年完全冇感覺既 <br />\n睇返自己10年前開過post 初戀女朋友過左身 <br />\n10年後既今日 除左佢既家人 係咪其他人都遺忘左佢 <br />\n呢一刻初戀女朋友你又係邊度 <br />\n時間過咁快 自己生命其實都係倒數緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e37e03ee589d1cc2111812713b99dcad82aad81","tid":219221,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02e8f61b2a89271c0b71ef586e105770cca3d5c","tid":219221,"uid":65578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534314b6006a66f11ab8cfcd505e7f0f61d1cc25","tid":219221,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7fdb2a9f86c4a5e3b4c7f469160b7706cec7af","tid":219221,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"算吧啦"},{"pid":"393bc77d5a1373a4537023e589f1fbbba56619c6","tid":219221,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算吧啦</blockquote><br />\n人生冇意義了"},{"pid":"b3dd0c1476ae92308786a97f2062f2203e47ef52","tid":219221,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:07:06.000Z",